snippet.title: Luna3X | Digital release | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Luna-3X will come out digitally on September 26th!

“Only seven days remain to save this planet’s creatures and the world. This is Jonah and Luna’s story.”

Help giant Luna and Jonah the boy to rescue the planet’s Creatures together in a synchronized action game!

Play the tambourine to attract the creatures called Kemonon and Plan-Plan, as they are relaxed by the melody. You might even find rare Kemonon and Plan-Plan hiding in various places. Save as many as you can before the Great Tsunami hits!
